<p rend="chapter">2. Dasasikkhāpadaṃ</p>

<p rend="bodytext" n="1"><hi rend="paranum">1</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi> Pāṇātipātā veramaṇī-sikkhāpadaṃ <note>veramaṇīsikkhāpadaṃ (sī. syā.)</note> samādiyāmi.</p>

<p rend="bodytext" n="2"><hi rend="paranum">2</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi> Adinnādānā veramaṇī-sikkhāpadaṃ samādiyāmi.</p>

<p rend="bodytext" n="3"><hi rend="paranum">3</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi> Abrahmacariyā <pb ed="M" n="0.0002" /> veramaṇī-sikkhāpadaṃ samādiyāmi.</p>

<p rend="bodytext" n="4"><hi rend="paranum">4</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi> Musāvādā veramaṇī-sikkhāpadaṃ samādiyāmi.</p>

<p rend="bodytext" n="5"><hi rend="paranum">5</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi> Surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā veramaṇī-sikkhāpadaṃ samādiyāmi <pb ed="T" n="0.0002" />.</p>

<p rend="bodytext" n="6"><hi rend="paranum">6</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi> Vikālabhojanā veramaṇī-sikkhāpadaṃ samādiyāmi.</p>

<p rend="bodytext" n="7"><hi rend="paranum">7</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi> Nacca-gīta-vādita-visūkadassanā veramaṇī-sikkhāpadaṃ samādiyāmi.</p>

<p rend="bodytext" n="8"><hi rend="paranum">8</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi> Mālā-gandha-vilepana-dhāraṇa-maṇḍana-vibhūsanaṭṭhānā veramaṇī-sikkhāpadaṃ samādiyāmi.</p>

<p rend="bodytext" n="9"><hi rend="paranum">9</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi> Uccāsayana-mahāsayanā veramaṇī-sikkhāpadaṃ samādiyāmi.</p>

<p rend="bodytext" n="10"><hi rend="paranum">10</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi> Jātarūpa-rajatapaṭiggahaṇā <pb ed="P" n="0.0002" /> veramaṇī-sikkhāpadaṃ samādiyāmi.</p>

<p rend="centre">Dasasikkhāpadaṃ <note>dasasikkhāpadaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ (syā.)</note> niṭṭhitaṃ.</p>
